title: Vincent van Gogh Fishing in Spring, the Pont de Clichy (Asnières) Mug
description:
Mug developed from Vincent van Gogh’s Fishing in Spring, the Pont de Clichy (Asnières), 1887, from the Art Institute of Chicago’s collection.

A masterpiece from our collection can be enjoyed every day along with breakfast or afternoon tea!  A great gift for a fellow art lover.

  • Size: 12 oz.
  • Dimensions: 3.5 x 3.75 x 5 in.
  • Box Dimensions: 5.75 x 4.5 x 4.125 in.
  • Material: Porcelain
  • Microwave and Dishwasher Safe.
